    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/0079888ee0ab60ca79c0ccfb11a16525.avif?t=1768254592\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/d61842aededb1a661da4e4aed92888f4.poster.avif?t=1768254592\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/d61842aededb1a661da4e4aed92888f4.webm?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/d61842aededb1a661da4e4aed92888f4.mp4?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《允许开火》</strong>是一款拥有优秀物理效果和轻度战术元素的复古风直升机射击游戏。射击，躲避，在战场上移动你的小队，几乎一切都能用绳子和磁铁吊起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/a4040af75db13b0897c6cce994c6f883.poster.avif?t=1768254592\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/a4040af75db13b0897c6cce994c6f883.webm?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/a4040af75db13b0897c6cce994c6f883.mp4?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完全基于物理效果的操作，你可以发挥创造力，利用环境获得优势。用火箭让敌人在空中翻滚，或用绳子将岩石扔向敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/1a3073c8e502d53c14bdee005b7e9ace.poster.avif?t=1768254592\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/1a3073c8e502d53c14bdee005b7e9ace.webm?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/1a3073c8e502d53c14bdee005b7e9ace.mp4?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的小队运往敌占区，或安排他们防御自己的基地。明智地部署他们，完成你的目标，尽量别在路上落下太多人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/777f6550f5a8038eac1afe266e783ca6.poster.avif?t=1768254592\" width=1170 height=754 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/777f6550f5a8038eac1afe266e783ca6.webm?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/777f6550f5a8038eac1afe266e783ca6.mp4?t=1768254592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快动起来，重新引导热追踪导弹。带上坦克，让它协助进攻敌方基地。吊起敌人，送他们飞向死亡。你可以吊起一切未被固定的物体，尽情发挥创造力吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710820/extras/e6b9fc99447e252f3ff0ff216d49bcca.avif?t=1768254592\" width=600 height=89 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 完全基于物理特性，吊起载具、敌军或重新引导热追踪导弹，随机应变</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整单人战役</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买和升级直升机</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自定义配置</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3种环境：沙漠、丛林、极地</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日间和夜间任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种拥有物理效果的敌方载具：坦克、吉普车、小卡车、防空炮塔、船只和战斗机</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
